                  commercial properties, including but not limited to: <ul>
                    <li>Driveways</li><li>Sidewalks</li><li>Decks</li><li>
                      Patios
                    </li><li>Siding</li><li>Roofs</li>
                  </ul>
                </p>
              </li>

              <li>
                <h3>2. Booking and Payment</h3>
