                        otherwise agreed.
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        We accept cash, credit cards, and electronic payments.
                      </li>
                    </ul>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </li>

              <li>
                <h3>3. Cancellations and Rescheduling</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>
                    Cancellations must be made at least 24 hours in advance to
                    avoid a cancellation fee.
                  </li>
                  <li>Rescheduling is subject to availability.</li>
                </ul>
              </li>

              <li>
                <h3>4. Customer Responsibilities</h3>

                <ul>
                  <li>
                    Customers must provide access to the areas to be serviced.
                  </li>

