                  staff and property. Abstracts Power Wash is insured, but
                  customers are responsible for any damage to their property
                  during the service.
                </p>
              </li>

              <li>
                <h3>6. Warranty and Satisfaction Guarantee</h3>
                <p>
                  We strive for 100% customer satisfaction. If you are not
                  satisfied, please contact us within 48 hours, and we will
                  address your concerns.
                </p>
