              <li>
                <h3>9. Changes to Terms</h3>
                <p>
                  We reserve the right to modify these terms and conditions at
                  any time. Changes will be effective upon posting on our
                  website.
                </p>
              </li>

              <li>
                <h3>10. Contact Information</h3>
                <p>
                  For questions or concerns regarding these terms and
                  conditions, please contact us at: <ul>
                    <li>Abstracts Power Wash</li>
                    <li>[Your Email]</li>
